To register your application in Google Drive following next steps:

1. Use the link: [https://developers.facebook.com/](https://developers.facebook.com/).
2. Click the button &quot;Log In&quot;

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

1. Log in to Facebook
2. Click the button &quot;Add a New App&quot;

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

1. Fill all necessary fields in the Window &quot;Create a New App ID&quot;

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

1. Click the button Create App ID
2. In Settings of Facebook Login fill Valid OAuth Redirect URLs

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

1. In Basic Settings take App ID and App Secret for authorization in bNesis

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

For publication app and getting permissions  for calling some API you need to do following steps:

1. In settings app click button App Review:

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

2. Click on button &quot;Add Items&quot; and chose the necessary permissions following the instructions of Facebook:

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

3. Next you need fill out details:

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

4. Then wait for approval of Facebook.

5. For publication App you need click on checkbox &quot;Make bNesisAPI public?&quot;

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)
